The ACE jumped up, ontop of a skyscraper, and motioned with his free hand to get up there.  &quot;You just wait.&quot; he said, backjumping onto a nearby scraper as well.  They stood there for a second.  Then, missles blew out of the ACE's suits leg launcher, followed by another batch.  &quot;Homing!&quot; he said, staring at the screen which said 'lock-on'.  &quot;Ahhh @#%$!&quot; he said, back jumping again, firing like crazy.  He took out most of them, but was hit by a few.  &quot;Well, that was careless of me.&quot; he said smiling.  &quot;Time to die!&quot; he said, switching the machine gun to a small cannon rifle.  He fired a shot, jumping forward, he quickly drew his beam sword and slashed down.  Amazingly, the ACE had been hit, but was able to block the attack.  &quot;Your smarter than you look.&quot; Mike continued, falling to the ground, hovering, and then landed.  The ACE jumped down, headfirst with his jets on.  &quot;Idiot.&quot; Mike said, backpedaling a little, firing a shot.  It hit, but it didn't effect it at all.  &quot;Puh.&quot; Mike said, drawing his beam sword once more.  The ACE did the same once it landed.  The walked to each other, and then galloped at the last second, hitting the swords at full force.  The ACE backjumped, but Mike charged forward, hitting the enemy with his side.  &quot;I'm NOT ditching another weapon.&quot; he said, keeping his machine gun holstered on the suit's back.  The ACE got back up, and jumped foward.  &quot;Oh, so now your furious.  Good, that makes you an easy target, you'll be blinded by your madness!&quot; he said, easily sidestepping, slashing downward with his sword, cutting the ACE right in half.  &quot;They're easy today...must be rookies.&quot; he said, walking off in the explosion. <p>------<br>
