t; he said, falling to his feet.   He saw the soldier, and opened fire.  Two the chest and one to the head. (OOC: heh, always wanted to say that.)  &quot;Gah..&quot; he said, standing up slowly.  Central Command was only about 350 meters, and he could make it, if there wasn't any enemies.<br>
